s (literally) and the bear is safe to use again.\", \"from\": 3693, \"to\": 3788, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00a92025 GIZMODO USA LLC.\", \"from\": 3790, \"to\": 3812, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3804, \"end\": 3807, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9456170295194432, \"rank\": 0.0575105594011107, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 3808, \"end\": 3811, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Limited_liability_company\", \"score\": 0.9999903978152259, \"rank\": 9.602276869798315e-06, \"text\": \"LLC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Limited_liability_company\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Limited_liability_company\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All rights reserved.\", \"from\": 3814, \"to\": 3834, \"entities\": []}]}"